query:
SELECT 
  id,
  userId,
  domain,
  domainPrice,
  managementFee,
  totalPrice,
  status,
  stripePaymentIntentId,
  registrarOrderId,
  created_at,
  updated_at
FROM domain_orders
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 5;
